<li>Add support for extension compatibility <a href="https://github.com/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8081" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8081/hovercard">#8081</a></li>
<li>Improve PHP code with hook enums <a href="https://github.com/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8036" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8036/hovercard">#8036</a></li>
<li>New hook <code>nav_entries</code> <a href="https://github.com/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8054" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8054/hovercard">#8054</a></li>
<li>Rename <a href="https://github.com/FreshRSS/Extensions">Extensions</a> default branch from <em>master</em> to <em>main</em> <a href="https://github.com/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8194" data-hovercard-type="pull_request" data-hovercard-url="/FreshRSS/FreshRSS/pull/8194/hovercard">#8194</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
